<HEADLINE> Nepali PM Calls for Responsible Role of Mass Media </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, May 2 (Xinhua) -- Prime Minister Lokendra Bahadur
Chand today called on Nepali journalists to maintain sustainable
development of the mass communications sector by disseminating
reliable news to the public.
</P>
