<HEADLINE> COSCO to Bid for Major Development Project in HK </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 2 (Xinhua) -- Cosco (HK) Group says it will join
forces with one or more unidentified companies to bid for the 15
billion HK dollars (1.92 billion U.S. dollars) phase-two property
development at the local Mass Transit Railway Corp.'s airport
railway station in West Kowloon.
</P>
<P>
Today's South China Morning Post quoted a spokesman for Cosco
