residential apartments and not more than 1,776 car parking spaces.
It is part of the proposed seven-phase residential-office-hotel
complex in West Kowloon.
</P>
<P>
The Mass Transit Railway Corp. is inviting potential parties to
submit expressions of interest for the project by today and formal
tender invitations will begin in the third quarter of this year.
 
