<HEADLINE> John Major to Step Down as Conservative Leader </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, May 2 (Xinhua) -- Out-going British Prime Minnister
John Major announced today that he would step down as Conservative
leader. 
</P>
</TEXT>
