which he presented a letter containing the name of the Selangor
chief minister and the sultan consented to the name in the letter
signed by Prime Minister Mahathir Mohamad who is now in Malawi on
a three-day official visit.
</P>
<P>
Abu Hassan, 56, who is Selangor's deputy liaison committee
chairman of the ruling United Malays National Organization (UMNO),
resigned from the federal cabinet post today.
</P>
