Swiss Foreign Minister Flavio Cotti also held talks with Zou
today, saying that Switzerland and China have had good relations
and have gained remarkable achievements in their cooperation on
economy, trade, science and technology and culture. Switzerland is
willing to further develop its prospective relations with China,
he said.
</P>
